{"tid":1202693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失戀 有冇人可以金鐘m 記陪我傾心事","createTime":"2019-06-11T10:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T14:55:54.000Z","uid":33797,"like":113,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"839c5b2e6602e69c8ba3540eec327c7d29824b5d","tid":1202693,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"我一直覺得條港女有異心，尋日同條囡嘈完，明明佢郁手先，我還手佢大大力打鳩我。好啦，今日條女叫埋個契家佬嚟講數，抱到條女實一實，覺得我會打撚柒佢。真，我真係講過要打撚柒佢。屌你明明條柒婆勾佬想fake曬我d錢同你一齊，我真係想打柒個柒婆同個契家佬，但個契家佬好似好好打，個柒婆咀硬又閪硬，屌佢唔入，有冇朋友出嚟同我傾心事，點教訓個契家佬同柒婆，人在金鐘m 記無奈中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbc3c513d4d8e3e885520e3c0015faee29f139c","tid":1202693,"uid":33797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:09:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46443f2519fd66aa1c5f31d215928c5ab28cc30","tid":1202693,"uid":33797,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以理下我呢個毒撚"},{"pid":"364617531b251dc3ec47e3c3fd5a5bb11f528722","tid":1202693,"uid":33797,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"開導下我啦，你都有失戀嘅時候"},{"pid":"a2ad01d942a03831fb2931f45e0a7c97889b83cf","tid":1202693,"uid":33797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:13:31.000Z","msg":"金鐘m記毒撚冇人理"},{"pid":"1f3c119853d361492921a90dc32dfe9c4abbffd5","tid":1202693,"uid":200135,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:14:36.000Z","msg":"今晚一齊野餐心情可能會好啲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c06f9164bdd4e62b909dc633365b1c648e10da","tid":1202693,"uid":33797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:14:58.000Z","msg":"我可以點做，你又會點做，分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde88dd8c408b9911f851fd1eedfabc8ef431608","tid":1202693,"uid":33797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote